	Description = [[<p>The KartaVR "Open Folder" scripts make it easy to access the KartaVR tools, and the temporary files that are generated as the intermediate outputs from the various KartaVR pipeline scripts.</p>

<h2>How do I run these scripts?</h2>

<p>The "<a href="http://www.andrewhazelden.com/projects/kartavr/docs/scripts.html#open-containing-folder">Open Containing Folder</a>", "<a href="http://www.andrewhazelden.com/projects/kartavr/docs/scripts.html#open-temp-folder">Open KartaVR Temp Folder</a>", and "<a href="http://www.andrewhazelden.com/projects/kartavr/docs/scripts.html#open-vr-view-publishing-folder">Open VR View Publishing Folder</a>" Lua scripts are accessible in Fusion Standalone's "Script &gt; KartaVR &gt; Open Folder &gt;" menu. In Resolve the scripts can be accessed inside the Fusion page environment using the "Workspace &gt; Scripts &gt; KartaVR &gt; Open Folder &gt;" menu.</p>

<p>These Lua scripts are installed by Reactor to the local folder of:<br>
<a href="file://Reactor:/Deploy/Scripts/Comp/KartaVR/Open Folder/">Reactor:/Deploy/Scripts/Comp/KartaVR/Open Folder/</a></p>


